title: Phish 2013-07-27 - The Gorge, Quincy, WA
description:
Saturday, 07/27/2013 
Gorge Amphitheatre, George, WA

Set 1: Architect, Golgi Apparatus, The Curtain With, Kill Devil Falls > The Moma Dance > Maze, Beauty of a Broken Heart, Roses Are Free, Say Something[1], Ocelot, After Midnight

Set 2: Down with Disease[2] -> Undermind > Light -> Sneakin' Sally Through the Alley > Also Sprach Zarathustra > Walls of the Cave > Fluffhead > Run Like an Antelope

Encore: Show of Life, Good Times Bad Times

[1] Debut.
[2] Unfinished.

Performers: Trey Anastasio, Page McConnell, Jon Fishman, Mike Gordon
Notes: This show was webcast via LivePhish.com and featured the debut of the Mike Gordon/Scott Murawski-penned "Say Something." Disease was unfinished.
